<p>Veerle: Who knows?</p>
<p>Vitaly: ... she ended up going. Well, if you, the listener, would like to hear more from Veerle, you can find her on Twitter where she’s @vpieters, and also in home homepage, of course, which is veerle.duoh.com, veerle.duoh.com.</p>
<p>Veerle: I’m actually not much on Twitter anymore-</p>
