<h3>8:45 AM ET (<a href="https://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/fixedtime.html?msg=Figma%20Auto%20Layout%20Deep%20Dive&amp;iso=20230327T09&amp;p1=224&amp;ah=3&amp;am=00">Check your time zone</a> ⏰)</h3>
<p>Virtual doors open, registration, chat, and introductions.</p>
<h3>9:00 AM – 11:30 AM</h3>
<p>Deep dive into Figma responsive design, deep dive into constraints, auto layout, and, most importantly but rarely discussed, breakpoints for your UI design.</p>
<h3>11:30 AM – 12:30 PM</h3>
<p>Q&amp;A with Christine on the day’s material. Networking!</p>
<p>You can always re-watch the session at a more convenient time and follow the webinar at your own pace.</p>
