<li>“<a href="https://netflixtechblog.com/implementing-japanese-subtitles-on-netflix-c165fbe61989">Implementing Japanese Subtitles on Netflix</a>”, Rohit Puri, Cyril Concolato, David Ronca and Yumi Deeter</li>
